begin
  wwv_flow_api.create_qb_saved_query (
    p_id => 2437031679535684
    ,p_query_owner => 'PROJECTMANAGEMENT'
    ,p_title => 'increment_PK'
 ,p_qb_sql => 
'Drop sequence user_id_seq;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE SEQUENCE user_id_seq start with 1;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'Drop trigger user_bi;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE TRIGGER user_bi'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEFORE INSERT ON usera'||wwv_flow.LF||
'FOR EACH ROW'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEGIN'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'    if :NEW.USER_ID is null then '||wwv_flow.LF||
'    select user_id_seq.nextval into :NEW.USER_ID '||wwv_flow.LF||
'  FROM dual;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'  END IF;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'END;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'ALTER TRIGGER user_bi ENABLE;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'Drop sequence payment_id_seq;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE SEQUENCE payment_id_seq start with 1;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'Drop trigger paymen'||
't_bi;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE TRIGGER payment_bi'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEFORE INSERT ON payment'||wwv_flow.LF||
'FOR EACH ROW'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEGIN'||wwv_flow.LF||
' if :NEW.PAYMENT_ID is null then '||wwv_flow.LF||
'    select payment_id_seq.nextval into :NEW.PAYMENT_ID'||wwv_flow.LF||
'  FROM dual;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'  END IF;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'END;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'ALTER TRIGGER  payment_bi ENABLE;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'Drop sequence cart_id_seq;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE SEQUENCE cart_id_seq start with 1;'||wwv_flow.LF||
''||wwv_flow.LF||
'Drop trigger cart_bi;'||wwv_flow.LF||
'CREATE TRIGGER cart_bi'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEFORE INSERT ON cart'||wwv_flow.LF||
'FOR EACH ROW'||wwv_flow.LF||
'BEGIN'||wwv_flow.LF||
'  if :NEW.CART'||
